Title: Series: Vie et oeuvres des peintres les plus célèbres de toutes les écoles
Description: The Flight into Egypt, after Domenichino; in outline; proof before letter. c.1805/25 Engraving
Curator's comments: From "Vies Et Oeuvres Des Peintres Les Plus Célèbres De Toutes Les Ecoles", a series of outline engravings with accompanying text by Charles Paul Landon, published in several volumes c.1805/25. Plates 1891,0511.345 to 393 all belong to this series. The initial of the name cannot be read, nor can the engraver be identified.
